parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A cracked dashboard over the passenger airbag can cause the airbag to deploy unexpectedly or not deploy properly in the event of an accident, which can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: Cracks in the dashboard over the passenger airbag
cracks in a square or circle shape
airbag exposed in the dashboard
jagged edges
and weakened dashboard structure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The TAKATA airbag recall issues can cause the airbag to deploy unexpectedly or not deploy properly in the event of an accident, which can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: Fuel leak
faulty and defective airbag
airbag deployment issues
and recall repair issues.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Airbag deployment issues can cause the airbag to not deploy properly in the event of an accident, which can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: Airbag did not deploy in an accident
airbag deployed unexpectedly
and airbag deployment issues.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch pedal assembly can cause the clutch pedal to snap or break, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal snaps or breaks while driving
the clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering column can cause loss of control, making it difficult or impossible to steer the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The steering column moves while in the locked position
pieces of the steering column break and fall
the steering wheel jerks or becomes hard to steer
especially when turning or at full lock.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electronic power steering rack can cause loss of control, making it difficult or impossible to steer the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The steering wheel jerks or becomes hard to steer
especially when turning or at full lock
the power steering reduces or becomes more difficult to turn when off-center.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch pedal bracket can cause difficulty or inability to shift gears, leading to loss of control, accidents, or injuries.
symptoms: The clutch pedal bracket breaks
causing considerable difficulty in safely driving the car
the clutch pedal becomes hard to press or sticks to the floor.
